{"tid":1866660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大粒墨自首未？","createTime":"2020-02-06T22:34:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T23:08:42.000Z","uid":126606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6805b2528c53999c66edd289984a9bc66793b62d","tid":1866660,"uid":126606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T22:34:55.000Z","msg":"訓左冇睇，佢心情好返未，準備好自首？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2741901cd8d4f31e5657e01f6096095000b38603","tid":1866660,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T22:37:18.000Z","msg":"琴日回應左<br />\n<br />\n管浩鳴:陳同佳返台計劃待疫情紓緩再作打算<br />\n<br />\n承認在台殺害港人女友潘曉穎的陳同佳，自去年10月中旬在港出獄後杳無音訊、一直未返回台灣受審；協助陳同佳出獄的香港聖公會教省秘書長管浩鳴承認，對方的返台計劃會在新型肺炎疫情紓緩後才再作打算。<br />\n<br />\n台灣外交部今日宣布，所有近14日曾入境中港澳人士暫緩入境，亦不再受理相關簽證申請；陳同佳在去年出獄後，據報於管浩鳴安排下住在警方安全屋，至今已逾3個月無露面。<br />\n<br />\n管浩鳴被傳媒問及對方最新去向時表示：「相信港台兩地都把抵抗疫症放於首位」，一切留待疫症過後再作解決。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2372373/管浩鳴%3A陳同佳返台計劃待疫情紓緩再作打算\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2372373%2F%E7%AE%A1%E6%B5%A9%E9%B3%B4%253A%E9%99%B3%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%B3%E8%BF%94%E5%8F%B0%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E5%BE%85%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E7%B4%93%E7%B7%A9%E5%86%8D%E4%BD%9C%E6%89%93%E7%AE%97&d=zpo3oWyV3xTDIRTZ1PVZWcg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=629466da\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2372373/管浩鳴%3A陳同佳返台計劃待疫情紓緩再作打算</a>"},{"pid":"3d5dbec72b96bfae2e6b6ed2e0bb3a6ea63ba0c2","tid":1866660,"uid":41988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T22:49:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AnJ0Z6b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAnJ0Z6b.jpg&h=eef06823&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e12db512b0d7b513a0ae0ad10041c7e0cb9ba77","tid":1866660,"uid":128102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T23:08:42.000Z","msg":"係安全屋晚晚攬女鋸扒笑9你地香港人 自首不了"}